An awesome classic casual game collection includes match game, vegetable slot machine, catch game and cast game at the same time. Each game matches with a different story and these four game compose the whole amazing FarmStory.

Match Same Buddy - Encounter heavy rain, lively vegetable jumps out of car now. Move your basket back and forth to catch those sprites.
Vegetable Slot Machine - Entertain on gaming machine by earned coins. Amazing reward is oncoming when fortune wheel stops.

Catch Runaway Sprite - Cast cute running vegetable into opposite box on conveyor. Cast the requested vegetable to double your score.
Cast Cute Guys - Vegetable prefers shower with identical buddy to strange guys. 

Connect them at least 3 a group in tub. Classic match game starts your puzzle adventure.

Features:

- Cute and exquisite art design, feast of finger practice
- Multiple background stories satisfy different game players
- Enjoy adorable farm adventure completely free
- Break time app, standalone game, play it offline

What's New:

- Adjust games layout and play order to optimize gameplay
- Fix some bugs
